index.php/Battle_at_the_Mander\" title=\"Battle at the Mander\">Battle at the Mander</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Sack_of_King%27s_Landing\" title=\"Sack of King&#39;s Landing\">Sack of King's Landing</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Siege_of_Storm%27s_End\" title=\"Siege of Storm&#39;s End\">Siege of Storm's End</a><sup>1</sup></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Combat_at_the_tower_of_joy\" title=\"Combat at the tower of joy\">Tower of joy</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Coronation_of_Robert_I_Baratheon\" title=\"Coronation of Robert I Baratheon\">Robert's coronation</a></li></ul>\n</div></td></tr><tr style=\"height:2px\"><td></td></tr><tr><td scope=\"row\" class=\"navbox-group\" style=\";;\"><a href=\"/index.php/284_AC\" title=\"284 AC\">284&#160;AC</a></td><td style=\"text-align:left;border-left-width:2px;border-left-style:solid;width:100%;padding:0px;;;\" class=\"navbox-list navbox-odd\"><div style=\"padding:0em 0.25em\">\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Assault_on_Dragonstone\" title=\"Assault on Dragonstone\">Assault on Dragonstone</a><sup>2</sup></li></ul>\n</div></td></tr><tr style=\"height:2px;\"><td></td></tr><tr><td class=\"navbox-abovebelow\" style=\";\" colspan=\"2\"><div>\n<ul><li><sup>1</sup>The siege started in 282 AC and ended in 283 AC.</li>\n<li><sup>2</sup>Even though this event is associated with the rebellion, it technically occurred after Robert's Rebellion.</li></ul>\n</div></td></tr></tbody></table></td></tr></tbody></table>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403115644\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.077 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.230 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 923/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 16399/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 20900/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 4084/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 17/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 1918/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0